Mr. Odland was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Office Depot, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by AutoZone, Inc., Chief Operating Officer by Ahold USA, Inc., President-Foodservice Division by Sara Lee Bakery Group, Inc., Vice President by The Quaker Oats Co., Adjunct Professor by Fau College of Business, and Adjunct Professor by Lynn University, Inc. 
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Notre Dame and a graduate degree from Northwestern University.



